Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Balacbac Agro-Industrial School in the Municipality of Kapangan, Province of Benguet, to Governor Bado Dangwa Agro-Industrial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 720
An Act Changing the Name of the Balacbac Agro-Industrial School in the Municipality of Kapangan, Province of Benguet, to Governor Bado Dangwa Agro-Industrial School
Section 1. The name of the Balacbac Agro-Industrial School in the Municipality of Kapangan, Province of Benguet, is changed to Governor Bado Dangwa Agro-Industrial School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
